commitResults.messageBody: Replace check for null with instanceof

After a search online, a null check is preferred over instanceof as !=null can be applied to all objects in Java while instanceof may cause problems with primitive types.
Ref: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/30125548/why-or-why-not-use-instanceof-to-check-if-not-null
